WEBVTT

00:00:05.806 --> 00:00:08.141 line:80%
[♪ pop music playing]

00:00:50.058 --> 00:00:53.770 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:01:04.656 --> 00:01:05.782 line:80%
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

00:01:05.866 --> 00:01:07.784 line:80%
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

00:01:08.785 --> 00:01:10.787 line:80%
[♪ tender music plays]

00:01:23.174 --> 00:01:25.010 line:80%
[I-AN] You said you'd let me fly.

00:01:25.093 --> 00:01:26.511 line:80%
Why are you the one flying?

00:01:28.221 --> 00:01:30.223 line:80%
Let's switch. I can hold you.

00:01:30.974 --> 00:01:32.475 line:80%
-Forget it.
-Why not? Come on…

00:01:32.559 --> 00:01:33.935 line:80%
[yelps]

00:01:34.519 --> 00:01:36.438 line:80%
-[grunts]
-[Huiju yelps]

00:01:36.521 --> 00:01:37.772 line:80%
[Huiju pants]

00:01:39.983 --> 00:01:41.902 line:80%
[distorted breath]

00:01:41.985 --> 00:01:43.486 line:80%
[distorted exhale]

00:01:43.570 --> 00:01:44.821 line:80%
[Huiju grunts]

00:01:47.198 --> 00:01:48.283 line:80%
[gasps]

00:01:50.869 --> 00:01:52.871 line:80%
[♪ gentle pop music plays]

00:01:56.708 --> 00:01:57.959 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:01:58.627 --> 00:02:00.086 line:80%
Are you hurt anywhere?

00:02:07.010 --> 00:02:08.511 line:80%
You said I can do whatever I want.

00:03:23.712 --> 00:03:28.717 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:03:29.300 --> 00:03:30.844 line:20%
EPISODE 7

00:03:33.638 --> 00:03:34.639 line:20%
[I-AN clears throat]

00:03:45.442 --> 00:03:47.444 line:20%
-[Youngseon] Your Ladyship!
-[Yeongmun] Your Royal Highness.

00:03:48.403 --> 00:03:51.740 line:20%
Why were you out so late
without the Royal Guard?

00:03:53.033 --> 00:03:55.160 line:20%
Well, we were… You know…

00:03:55.243 --> 00:03:58.121 line:80%
They must have wanted some alone time.

00:03:58.204 --> 00:03:59.831 line:80%
[Youngseon chuckles]

00:03:59.914 --> 00:04:01.916 line:80%
Did you go somewhere nice?

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:03.418 line:80%
-No!
-No!

00:04:07.464 --> 00:04:08.590 line:80%
[sighs]

00:04:09.549 --> 00:04:11.426 line:80%
He wanted some fresh air,

00:04:12.510 --> 00:04:14.596 line:80%
so we went for a drive. Beep-beep.

00:04:15.138 --> 00:04:17.474 line:80%
Then you should've let us know!

00:04:17.557 --> 00:04:20.518 line:80%
Aide Choi is a complete mess
because you two weren't reachable.

00:04:20.602 --> 00:04:21.603 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:04:26.441 --> 00:04:27.442 line:80%
Listen.

00:04:28.568 --> 00:04:29.861 line:80%
-You should…
-Pardon?

00:04:29.944 --> 00:04:31.780 line:80%
-What? Huh?
-Yes?

00:04:36.534 --> 00:04:37.827 line:80%
You should get some rest.

00:04:37.911 --> 00:04:39.120 line:80%
[♪ playful music playing]

00:04:39.204 --> 00:04:40.497 line:80%
Aren't you tired?

00:04:41.915 --> 00:04:43.249 line:80%
I am.

00:04:45.085 --> 00:04:46.503 line:80%
Gosh, I'm so tired.

00:05:05.522 --> 00:05:07.524 line:80%
[♪ gentle music plays]

00:05:12.737 --> 00:05:14.197 line:80%
[exclaims quietly]

00:05:14.280 --> 00:05:15.365 line:80%
[sighs]

00:05:26.167 --> 00:05:27.710 line:80%
[muffled exclaiming]

00:05:30.171 --> 00:05:31.256 line:80%
[pants]

00:05:32.465 --> 00:05:34.467 line:80%
I mean, it's no big deal.

00:05:34.551 --> 00:05:36.719 line:80%
We were just caught up in the moment.

00:05:36.803 --> 00:05:38.096 line:80%
I mean, it's not like

00:05:38.680 --> 00:05:39.848 line:80%
I threw myself at him.

00:05:40.640 --> 00:05:41.641 line:80%
Hmm.

00:05:43.768 --> 00:05:45.603 line:80%
[sighs]

00:05:47.605 --> 00:05:48.690 line:80%
[whimpers]

00:05:49.607 --> 00:05:51.359 line:80%
[squeakily] Why did I do that?

00:06:11.045 --> 00:06:12.046 line:80%
[gasps]

00:06:17.510 --> 00:06:18.636 line:80%
[chuckles softly]

00:06:38.323 --> 00:06:39.449 line:80%
It's fine.

00:06:39.532 --> 00:06:41.492 line:80%
You're a grown,
functioning member of society.

00:06:41.576 --> 00:06:42.827 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:06:42.911 --> 00:06:44.746 line:80%
It's not fine at all!

00:06:44.829 --> 00:06:47.749 line:80%
I'm so screwed. What am I going to do now?

00:06:47.832 --> 00:06:49.459 line:80%
[footsteps outside]

00:06:57.217 --> 00:06:58.343 line:80%
[I-AN clears throat]

00:06:59.469 --> 00:07:00.470 line:80%
Seong Huiju.

00:07:02.931 --> 00:07:03.973 line:80%
[whispers] What now?

00:07:16.110 --> 00:07:17.111 line:80%
[chuckles softly]

00:07:20.698 --> 00:07:21.699 line:80%
[chuckles softly]

00:07:31.209 --> 00:07:32.835 line:80%
[sighs]

00:07:39.342 --> 00:07:40.760 line:80%
[heartbeat thumping]

00:07:40.843 --> 00:07:42.762 line:80%
Are you nuts? Why are you racing?

00:07:42.845 --> 00:07:43.930 line:80%
[clicks tongue]

00:07:46.307 --> 00:07:47.642 line:80%
[sighs]

00:07:59.988 --> 00:08:00.989 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:08:01.072 --> 00:08:02.949 line:80%
[yelps]

00:08:04.701 --> 00:08:06.703 line:80%
[♪ dreamy music playing]

00:08:24.262 --> 00:08:25.388 line:80%
Off to work already?

00:08:29.017 --> 00:08:29.851 line:80%
Oh!

00:08:29.934 --> 00:08:31.853 line:80%
[chuckling] Yes, that's right.

00:08:31.936 --> 00:08:34.188 line:80%
I need to get to work.

00:08:34.272 --> 00:08:36.607 line:80%
I need to work. I'm the CEO.

00:08:36.691 --> 00:08:39.569 line:80%
Need to figure out my successor and all.
This and that.

00:08:40.403 --> 00:08:41.904 line:80%
What a lovely day it is today.

00:08:41.988 --> 00:08:43.072 line:80%
See you.

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:55.209 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:08:58.254 --> 00:08:59.297 line:80%
[church bell tolls]

00:08:59.380 --> 00:09:01.257 line:80%
[♪ organ music plays]

00:09:05.970 --> 00:09:09.682 line:80%
In the name of the Father,
the Son, and the Holy Spirit,

00:09:09.766 --> 00:09:10.892 line:80%
Amen.

00:09:11.476 --> 00:09:12.477 line:80%
Amen.

00:09:13.061 --> 00:09:14.771 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:09:14.854 --> 00:09:15.855 line:80%
You see,

00:09:16.731 --> 00:09:19.484 line:80%
I'm actually not Catholic. Is that okay?

00:09:20.360 --> 00:09:22.862 line:80%
Well, the man upstairs is a forgiving one.

00:09:23.446 --> 00:09:24.447 line:80%
Please go ahead.

00:09:24.530 --> 00:09:25.948 line:80%
[sighs]

00:09:26.449 --> 00:09:28.034 line:80%
Then, by chance,

00:09:28.117 --> 00:09:30.161 line:80%
do you think I could get an exorcism?

00:09:30.244 --> 00:09:31.162 line:80%
Pardon me?

00:09:32.538 --> 00:09:33.539 line:80%
It's just that…

00:09:34.290 --> 00:09:36.334 line:80%
I feel like I'm possessed right now.

00:09:41.089 --> 00:09:42.799 line:80%
[whimpering]

00:09:42.882 --> 00:09:44.133 line:80%
Oh no!

00:09:45.301 --> 00:09:47.720 line:80%
Could we maybe work something out?

00:09:47.804 --> 00:09:50.556 line:80%
I can make a very generous donation
to the church.

00:09:51.349 --> 00:09:52.642 line:80%
[gasps]

00:09:54.102 --> 00:09:55.269 line:80%
[whimpers]

00:09:56.854 --> 00:09:57.855 line:80%
[Huiju] Seriously?

00:09:58.356 --> 00:09:59.899 line:80%
"Not one to begrudge"?

00:09:59.982 --> 00:10:01.901 line:80%
Yet he just did that.

00:10:02.402 --> 00:10:03.903 line:80%
I even wore white for this.

00:10:06.447 --> 00:10:07.365 line:80%
Seong Huiju?

00:10:07.448 --> 00:10:08.908 line:80%
Oh.

00:10:08.991 --> 00:10:10.076 line:80%
Jeongwoo.

00:10:10.159 --> 00:10:11.702 line:80%
[chuckles softly]

00:10:11.786 --> 00:10:12.912 line:80%
What brings you here?

00:10:14.080 --> 00:10:15.081 line:80%
Oh, a cab.

00:10:15.164 --> 00:10:16.791 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:10:16.874 --> 00:10:19.335 line:80%
That's not what I'm asking.
Why are you here?

00:10:20.378 --> 00:10:22.004 line:80%
I thought you weren't religious.

00:10:23.881 --> 00:10:24.924 line:80%
I know, right?

00:10:28.261 --> 00:10:29.637 line:80%
Wait here. I'll be right out.

00:10:30.430 --> 00:10:31.681 line:80%
No, I can just go

00:10:32.306 --> 00:10:33.307 line:80%
by myself…

00:10:37.103 --> 00:10:38.688 line:80%
[sighs]

00:10:38.771 --> 00:10:40.398 line:80%
[phone buzzing]

00:10:41.732 --> 00:10:43.443 line:80%
PRINCE

00:10:46.446 --> 00:10:47.655 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:10:48.614 --> 00:10:50.700 line:80%
[vocalizes]

00:10:50.783 --> 00:10:51.784 line:80%
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

00:10:51.868 --> 00:10:53.327 line:80%
Are you free?

00:10:54.454 --> 00:10:55.455 line:80%
Right now?

00:10:55.538 --> 00:10:57.999 line:80%
We have something on the calendar
for wedding planning,

00:10:58.082 --> 00:10:59.542 line:80%
but you said you were busy.

00:10:59.625 --> 00:11:00.626 line:80%
<i>I see.</i>

00:11:01.711 --> 00:11:02.712 line:80%
Shall I reschedule it?

00:11:02.795 --> 00:11:04.088 line:80%
No, I have time.

00:11:04.172 --> 00:11:05.882 line:80%
Let's go, Huiju.

00:11:05.965 --> 00:11:07.216 line:80%
That was quick.

00:11:11.554 --> 00:11:14.307 line:80%
Your Royal Highness, I'll call you later.

00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:16.601 line:80%
See you later.

00:11:19.061 --> 00:11:21.731 line:80%
JUNIOR ALUM

00:11:22.732 --> 00:11:23.983 line:80%
[sighs]

00:11:24.066 --> 00:11:25.443 line:80%
Shall we?

00:11:28.946 --> 00:11:30.114 line:80%
I'm coming.

00:11:42.001 --> 00:11:43.503 line:80%
[Huiju] I told you,
I could've taken a cab.

00:11:44.879 --> 00:11:46.506 line:80%
It's fine. It's on the way anyway.

00:11:51.302 --> 00:11:52.553 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:11:52.637 --> 00:11:54.096 line:80%
Do you like driving too?

00:11:55.097 --> 00:11:56.557 line:80%
-That's random.
-The Grand Prince

00:11:56.641 --> 00:11:58.059 line:80%
smiles when he drives too.

00:11:58.726 --> 00:12:00.061 line:80%
He says it feels like he's flying.

00:12:00.770 --> 00:12:02.647 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:12:02.730 --> 00:12:04.732 line:80%
He can be so childlike sometimes.

00:12:08.569 --> 00:12:10.488 line:80%
[♪ gentle piano plays]

00:12:13.324 --> 00:12:14.659 line:80%
[sighs]

00:12:17.078 --> 00:12:20.665 line:20%
CASTLE BEAUTY

00:12:20.748 --> 00:12:22.166 line:80%
Bye. Thanks for the ride.

00:12:23.292 --> 00:12:24.794 line:80%
-Huiju.
-Yes?

00:12:25.878 --> 00:12:27.296 line:80%
Don't get too attached.

00:12:28.798 --> 00:12:29.966 line:80%
What?

00:12:30.591 --> 00:12:32.385 line:80%
It'll drive up the divorce settlement.

00:12:33.094 --> 00:12:34.679 line:80%
Be it in money, reputation…

00:12:36.639 --> 00:12:37.640 line:80%
or your heart.

00:12:43.980 --> 00:12:45.314 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:12:45.398 --> 00:12:47.275 line:80%
Do you think I'm an idiot?

00:12:48.276 --> 00:12:49.735 line:80%
-[chuckles softly]
-[scoffs]

00:12:49.819 --> 00:12:50.820 line:80%
Bye.

00:13:05.418 --> 00:13:06.460 line:80%
[sighs]

00:13:12.300 --> 00:13:13.342 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:13:13.426 --> 00:13:15.094 line:80%
Who does he take me for?

00:13:15.595 --> 00:13:17.763 line:80%
Someone who can't distinguish
between business and pleasure?

00:13:17.847 --> 00:13:18.848 line:80%
Seriously?

00:13:18.931 --> 00:13:20.141 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:13:22.310 --> 00:13:23.311 line:80%
[Hyejeong] Ms. Seong.

00:13:23.394 --> 00:13:25.980 line:80%
Pull the affiliate numbers
and line them up by revenue.

00:13:27.064 --> 00:13:28.065 line:80%
Throw this out for me.

00:13:28.149 --> 00:13:29.150 line:80%
[door opens]

00:13:35.072 --> 00:13:36.407 line:80%
[Hyejeong] Why, all of a sudden?

00:13:36.991 --> 00:13:39.160 line:80%
They must all be thrilled
that I'm stepping down.

00:13:39.660 --> 00:13:42.371 line:80%
Planning to slack off
without the revenue-obsessed boss

00:13:42.455 --> 00:13:43.664 line:80%
breathing down their necks.

00:13:44.540 --> 00:13:46.334 line:80%
So you want to whip them into shape?

00:13:46.417 --> 00:13:47.668 line:80%
Yes.

00:13:47.752 --> 00:13:49.170 line:80%
[♪ dramatic music plays]

00:13:49.253 --> 00:13:52.590 line:80%
I'll remind them they'll be
royally screwed if revenue drops.

00:13:56.552 --> 00:13:58.095 line:80%
Okay, I'll get to it now.

00:13:58.179 --> 00:13:59.639 line:80%
Have Seong Taeju meet me there.

00:13:59.722 --> 00:14:01.098 line:80%
The Senior Managing Director?

00:14:04.685 --> 00:14:06.979 line:20%
AUSPICIOUS DATES
FOR GRAND PRINCE I-AN'S WEDDING

00:14:08.856 --> 00:14:11.317 line:80%
These are the dates
the Royal Secretariat and the Cabinet

00:14:11.400 --> 00:14:13.361 line:80%
have proposed
for the Grand Prince's nuptials.

00:14:14.111 --> 00:14:15.237 line:80%
All are auspicious days,

00:14:15.321 --> 00:14:18.282 line:80%
so Your Majesty may select
whichever you see fit.

00:14:23.663 --> 00:14:26.540 line:80%
[announcer] Your Majesty,
Grand Prince I-AN has arrived.

00:14:26.624 --> 00:14:28.334 line:80%
Show him in.

00:14:36.425 --> 00:14:37.426 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:14:39.595 --> 00:14:41.931 line:80%
I heard you were selecting
the day for my nuptials.

00:14:43.516 --> 00:14:45.351 line:80%
I am considering choosing this date.

00:14:45.851 --> 00:14:46.894 line:80%
Is there a particular reason?

00:14:46.977 --> 00:14:49.438 line:80%
Is it not the earliest day?

00:14:49.522 --> 00:14:50.564 line:80%
[chuckles softly]

00:14:51.982 --> 00:14:53.317 line:80%
May I take a look?

00:14:54.652 --> 00:14:56.821 line:80%
[♪ pensive music plays]

00:15:04.662 --> 00:15:06.580 line:80%
I would prefer this day.

00:15:07.832 --> 00:15:09.417 line:80%
For any particular reason?

00:15:11.460 --> 00:15:12.461 line:80%
We will need…

00:15:14.547 --> 00:15:15.631 line:80%
some time.

00:15:18.384 --> 00:15:20.010 line:80%
I shall choose this date then.

00:15:23.723 --> 00:15:26.684 line:80%
JULY 3RD, LUNAR JUNE 9TH

00:15:31.397 --> 00:15:33.149 line:80%
[Huiju] I'm just here to support the team.

00:15:33.232 --> 00:15:35.192 line:80%
No need to be nervous.

00:15:36.444 --> 00:15:40.114 line:80%
You are our top-performing affiliate
in terms of sales.

00:15:41.657 --> 00:15:43.075 line:80%
The new collection that just launched

00:15:43.159 --> 00:15:45.911 line:80%
is performing well
with the 25-35 demographic.

00:15:46.495 --> 00:15:49.498 line:80%
This necklace is part of
the same set as your earrings today.

00:15:49.582 --> 00:15:51.000 line:80%
Would you like to try it on?

00:15:51.584 --> 00:15:52.585 line:80%
-Sure.
-All right.

00:16:01.844 --> 00:16:02.970 line:80%
Hmm…

00:16:03.053 --> 00:16:04.263 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:16:05.765 --> 00:16:08.601 line:80%
And it'll stay that way, right?

00:16:09.435 --> 00:16:10.436 line:80%
Pardon?

00:16:10.519 --> 00:16:12.062 line:80%
I don't think I'll ever stop

00:16:13.355 --> 00:16:14.774 line:80%
being curious about numbers.

00:16:18.068 --> 00:16:20.070 line:80%
I might be getting married,

00:16:20.613 --> 00:16:23.282 line:80%
but I'll still be keeping an eye
and ear on things.

00:16:24.450 --> 00:16:26.535 line:80%
Of course, ma'am.
We'll continue doing our best.

00:16:26.619 --> 00:16:27.745 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:16:28.579 --> 00:16:30.206 line:80%
Huiju.

00:16:34.376 --> 00:16:36.295 line:80%
Did I ask you to invite that gremlin too?

00:16:36.378 --> 00:16:37.671 line:80%
It wasn't me.

00:16:37.755 --> 00:16:38.839 line:80%
[Dayeong giggles]

00:16:42.301 --> 00:16:44.345 line:80%
I insisted on coming along.

00:16:44.428 --> 00:16:46.138 line:80%
I missed you, you know.

00:16:46.222 --> 00:16:48.682 line:80%
You could've just called
if you had something to say.

00:16:48.766 --> 00:16:50.476 line:80%
Making me come all this way…
[clicks tongue]

00:16:50.559 --> 00:16:53.229 line:80%
Babe, check this out.
This would look perfect on you.

00:16:53.896 --> 00:16:56.023 line:80%
Come on. This new collection is nice.

00:16:56.106 --> 00:16:57.316 line:80%
Try this on.

00:16:58.400 --> 00:16:59.360 line:80%
It's… Whoa, amazing.

00:16:59.443 --> 00:17:00.986 line:80%
This will be the first handover.

00:17:01.070 --> 00:17:02.571 line:80%
What?

00:17:03.489 --> 00:17:04.865 line:80%
My shares.

00:17:06.575 --> 00:17:07.576 line:80%
Right, your shares…

00:17:08.828 --> 00:17:09.954 line:80%
What?

00:17:10.704 --> 00:17:11.705 line:80%
Wait.

00:17:11.789 --> 00:17:13.249 line:80%
[♪ jazz music plays]

00:17:13.332 --> 00:17:14.834 line:80%
You mean it?

00:17:14.917 --> 00:17:17.419 line:80%
You're really going to hand it over
to me? All of Castle Beauty?

00:17:17.503 --> 00:17:19.421 line:80%
-Should I not?
-You should.

00:17:20.256 --> 00:17:22.758 line:80%
Come on. Why would you say such a thing?

00:17:22.842 --> 00:17:25.344 line:80%
-I will kill you if you fail.
-What?

00:17:25.427 --> 00:17:27.012 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:17:27.096 --> 00:17:28.722 line:80%
You heard me.

00:17:28.806 --> 00:17:30.474 line:80%
[mouthing] I will kill you.

00:17:39.733 --> 00:17:42.778 line:80%
Is that brat setting a trap to murder me?

00:17:43.696 --> 00:17:44.697 line:80%
No.

00:17:45.531 --> 00:17:46.407 line:80%
No?

00:17:46.490 --> 00:17:48.492 line:80%
Yeah, definitely not.

00:17:54.206 --> 00:17:55.332 line:80%
Did you really mean that?

00:17:56.250 --> 00:17:57.251 line:80%
What?

00:17:57.334 --> 00:18:00.087 line:80%
You have other options,
like hiring a non-owner executive.

00:18:00.170 --> 00:18:01.463 line:80%
There's also Director Choi.

00:18:01.547 --> 00:18:02.882 line:80%
It sounds like

00:18:03.674 --> 00:18:05.885 line:80%
you never want me to come back.

00:18:07.344 --> 00:18:10.848 line:80%
-What?
-Father and everyone will finally get it

00:18:10.931 --> 00:18:13.142 line:80%
once Seong Taeju takes over.

00:18:13.225 --> 00:18:14.685 line:80%
"Oh, right.

00:18:14.768 --> 00:18:17.980 line:80%
Seong Huiju is leagues above Seong Taeju.

00:18:18.689 --> 00:18:21.066 line:80%
Thus, the Castle Group successor must be

00:18:21.150 --> 00:18:24.194 line:80%
Seong Huiju and no one else."

00:18:24.278 --> 00:18:25.571 line:80%
I see.

00:18:25.654 --> 00:18:27.239 line:80%
Which affiliate is next?

00:18:32.745 --> 00:18:34.288 line:80%
Since when were they an affiliate?

00:18:35.539 --> 00:18:38.792 line:80%
I was told you confirmed it.
Were they wrong?

00:18:38.876 --> 00:18:39.919 line:80%
When?

00:18:40.002 --> 00:18:41.378 line:80%
-This morning.
-When did I…

00:18:41.462 --> 00:18:43.130 line:80%
<i>-Are you free?</i>
<i>-I have time.</i>

00:18:43.213 --> 00:18:44.214 line:80%
I did that.

00:18:45.382 --> 00:18:46.675 line:80%
I most certainly did.

00:18:46.759 --> 00:18:47.968 line:80%
Seriously?

00:18:48.052 --> 00:18:49.053 line:80%
Let's go.

00:18:51.472 --> 00:18:52.890 line:80%
[sighs]

00:18:52.973 --> 00:18:54.099 line:80%
[whimpers softly]

00:18:56.518 --> 00:18:57.519 line:80%
What the…

00:18:58.270 --> 00:18:59.396 line:80%
You're unbelievable.

00:19:24.129 --> 00:19:25.130 line:80%
How pretty.

00:19:26.090 --> 00:19:28.384 line:80%
This will be your wedding robe,

00:19:28.467 --> 00:19:31.053 line:80%
so please let us know right away
if you feel any discomfort.

00:19:31.136 --> 00:19:32.680 line:80%
-Sure.
-Please take your place.

00:19:36.892 --> 00:19:38.143 line:80%
Ms. Do.

00:20:24.857 --> 00:20:26.567 line:80%
-Can you turn to the right?
-Sure.

00:20:37.953 --> 00:20:38.954 line:80%
[Huiju] Hmm?

00:20:39.830 --> 00:20:40.831 line:80%
Oh!

00:20:40.914 --> 00:20:42.291 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:20:43.375 --> 00:20:44.376 line:80%
Stay still.

00:21:03.062 --> 00:21:04.271 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:21:06.398 --> 00:21:08.067 line:80%
-[Lady Choi] Are you feeling unwell?
-What?

00:21:08.150 --> 00:21:09.526 line:80%
-[Hyejeong] Are you sick?
-Royal Physician!

00:21:09.610 --> 00:21:10.903 line:80%
-What's wrong?
-No, I'm fine.

00:21:10.986 --> 00:21:12.905 line:80%
-Oh!
-What is it?

00:21:12.988 --> 00:21:15.157 line:80%
No, I'm just feeling
a little hot. That's all.

00:21:15.240 --> 00:21:17.367 line:80%
No, I think you have a fever.

00:21:17.451 --> 00:21:19.536 line:80%
I'm just a little hot. Too many layers.

00:21:19.620 --> 00:21:21.413 line:80%
Her Ladyship is overheated.
Lower the room temperature.

00:21:21.497 --> 00:21:22.706 line:80%
Yes, ma'am.

00:21:22.790 --> 00:21:24.374 line:80%
-Please hurry.
-No, I…

00:21:24.458 --> 00:21:25.876 line:80%
It will be cooler in no time.

00:21:26.877 --> 00:21:28.837 line:80%
Isn't it time for our next appointment?

00:21:28.921 --> 00:21:29.963 line:80%
[Hyeon] Your next appointment?

00:21:30.047 --> 00:21:32.841 line:80%
After this, a royal physician
will come by for a health assessment.

00:21:32.925 --> 00:21:35.094 line:80%
Tomorrow, we have dinner
at Ms. Seong's family home.

00:21:35.177 --> 00:21:37.096 line:80%
What? "Family home"?

00:21:37.971 --> 00:21:40.557 line:80%
As in <i>my </i>family? Why?

00:21:41.141 --> 00:21:44.561 line:80%
It's customary for a future son-in-law
to offer his greetings to his in-laws.

00:21:47.898 --> 00:21:48.899 line:80%
Mmm.

00:21:49.525 --> 00:21:52.319 line:80%
Ah. The chairman's office was notified.

00:21:52.402 --> 00:21:53.821 line:80%
They already confirmed it.

00:21:53.904 --> 00:21:55.030 line:80%
[Hyeon] Thank you.

00:21:55.114 --> 00:21:58.242 line:80%
I'm off to handle the Marriage Proposal
and Wedding Gift Delivery ceremonies.

00:21:58.742 --> 00:22:00.452 line:80%
Marriage Proposal ceremony?

00:22:01.036 --> 00:22:04.498 line:80%
Marriage Proposal
and Wedding Gift Delivery ceremonies?

00:22:05.916 --> 00:22:08.043 line:80%
[♪ ethereal music plays]

00:22:25.269 --> 00:22:27.938 line:80%
"This is a royal edict
for Hyeonguk of the Seong Family.

00:22:28.564 --> 00:22:29.606 line:80%
The King proclaimed…"

00:22:29.690 --> 00:22:31.733 line:80%
"When Heaven and Earth first parted,

00:22:31.817 --> 00:22:33.527 line:80%
human order came into being.

00:22:33.610 --> 00:22:37.156 line:80%
Through the union of husband and wife,
the ancestors and royal line are upheld."

00:22:47.249 --> 00:22:48.834 line:80%
Hand me another piece of paper.

00:22:48.917 --> 00:22:49.960 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:22:56.758 --> 00:22:58.510 line:80%
<i>In accordance with tradition,</i>

00:22:58.594 --> 00:23:01.972 line:80%
<i>Chief Attendant Min Jeongwoo</i>
<i>and Deputy Attendant Choi Hyeon</i>

00:23:02.055 --> 00:23:05.142 line:80%
<i>shall observe proper decorum</i>
<i>and carry out the Marriage Proposal.</i>

00:23:05.225 --> 00:23:08.187 line:80%
[Hyeon] "Thus is the royal edict.
Let all be duly informed."

00:23:29.917 --> 00:23:32.127 line:80%
I will now outline the proceedings.

00:23:32.628 --> 00:23:33.962 line:80%
Traditionally, the wedding rites

00:23:34.046 --> 00:23:36.882 line:80%
begin at the bride's home.

00:23:36.965 --> 00:23:39.051 line:80%
However, given the security risks

00:23:39.134 --> 00:23:41.511 line:80%
and His Royal Highness's regency,
they will instead be held

00:23:41.595 --> 00:23:43.055 line:80%
at his private residence.

00:23:43.931 --> 00:23:46.225 line:80%
Then we'll be
at his private residence as well?

00:23:46.308 --> 00:23:48.227 line:80%
Yes, that's right. [chuckles]

00:23:49.061 --> 00:23:51.813 line:80%
And I also have this for you…

00:23:51.897 --> 00:23:53.899 line:80%
Just a moment.

00:23:55.609 --> 00:23:58.946 line:80%
I put together an outline
of the wedding rites, just in case.

00:23:59.029 --> 00:24:00.530 line:80%
[Hyeonguk] Can you

00:24:00.614 --> 00:24:02.115 line:80%
speak a bit faster?

00:24:04.117 --> 00:24:06.828 line:80%
-Pardon?
-I had to postpone two meetings for this.

00:24:07.829 --> 00:24:09.915 line:80%
Yes, sir. Here you go.

00:24:13.627 --> 00:24:15.629 line:80%
FATHER

00:24:18.006 --> 00:24:19.049 line:80%
Ms. Seong.

00:24:19.841 --> 00:24:20.842 line:80%
Hey.

00:24:20.926 --> 00:24:22.469 line:80%
They're all waiting for you.

00:24:24.721 --> 00:24:26.014 line:80%
[Lady Choi] Why have you stepped outside?

00:24:28.475 --> 00:24:29.476 line:80%
Are you still overheated?

00:24:30.394 --> 00:24:32.145 line:80%
No, it's not that.

00:24:32.229 --> 00:24:35.190 line:80%
Then you must return
for your health assessment.

00:24:36.817 --> 00:24:37.859 line:80%
Okay.

00:24:40.696 --> 00:24:42.072 line:80%
You will have

00:24:42.155 --> 00:24:44.324 line:80%
a more thorough exam
at Royal Seoul Hospital.

00:24:44.992 --> 00:24:47.828 line:80%
Today's examination will assess
constitution and fertility.

00:24:47.911 --> 00:24:49.246 line:80%
Pardon?

00:24:49.329 --> 00:24:50.622 line:80%
Yes?

00:24:53.208 --> 00:24:56.545 line:80%
Mmm… No, it's nothing. Please continue.

00:24:56.628 --> 00:25:00.215 line:80%
[Lady Choi chuckles]
Heirs are precious within the palace.

00:25:00.299 --> 00:25:03.677 line:80%
Once your health is duly confirmed,
arrangements for your union shall--

00:25:03.760 --> 00:25:05.012 line:80%
"Arrangements"?

00:25:06.805 --> 00:25:08.682 line:80%
What sort of arrangements?

00:25:09.641 --> 00:25:13.270 line:80%
The conjugal union symbolizes
the harmony of yin and yang.

00:25:13.353 --> 00:25:17.316 line:80%
Yin must flow to yang,
and yang must incline toward yin.

00:25:17.399 --> 00:25:19.192 line:80%
Once proper comportment facilitates that,

00:25:19.276 --> 00:25:21.028 line:80%
an auspicious day and hour shall be set…

00:25:21.111 --> 00:25:22.821 line:80%
-[physician] Hold on.
-What is it?

00:25:23.405 --> 00:25:25.324 line:80%
Her pulse is elevated.

00:25:25.907 --> 00:25:26.908 line:80%
Uh…

00:25:26.992 --> 00:25:28.785 line:80%
-Are you feeling unwell?
-[chuckles]

00:25:28.869 --> 00:25:30.037 line:80%
Wait, hold on.

00:25:30.120 --> 00:25:32.122 line:80%
Could this be
a post-accident complication?

00:25:32.205 --> 00:25:35.834 line:80%
[chuckling]
No, it's nothing like that. Be quiet.

00:25:35.917 --> 00:25:38.170 line:80%
[Lady Choi]
Then do you have a preexisting condition?

00:25:38.253 --> 00:25:41.423 line:80%
No, not at all.
No preexisting condition. [chuckles]

00:25:41.506 --> 00:25:42.841 line:80%
[I-AN] That is enough.

00:25:42.924 --> 00:25:44.634 line:80%
I wish to speak with her in private.

00:25:45.427 --> 00:25:46.428 line:80%
Give us the room.

00:25:47.346 --> 00:25:48.930 line:80%
[Lady Choi] Yes, Your Royal Highness.

00:25:55.562 --> 00:25:56.563 line:80%
[Huiju clears throat]

00:25:57.647 --> 00:25:59.232 line:80%
[hums]

00:25:59.316 --> 00:26:01.234 line:80%
[Huiju clears throat]

00:26:01.318 --> 00:26:02.527 line:80%
Something bothering you?

00:26:03.153 --> 00:26:04.154 line:80%
What?

00:26:05.447 --> 00:26:06.990 line:80%
You've been acting strangely.

00:26:07.074 --> 00:26:08.283 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:26:12.037 --> 00:26:13.997 line:80%
You're the one
who's been acting strangely.

00:26:14.956 --> 00:26:17.542 line:80%
-Me?
-You're being unnecessarily sweet to me.

00:26:18.251 --> 00:26:20.629 line:80%
While everyone was watching,

00:26:20.712 --> 00:26:22.297 line:80%
you, like, brushed
the hair out of my face.

00:26:22.381 --> 00:26:24.049 line:80%
And your eyes…

00:26:27.302 --> 00:26:31.098 line:80%
You keep looking at me
with those doe eyes.

00:26:31.181 --> 00:26:32.557 line:80%
My eyes have never changed.

00:26:32.641 --> 00:26:33.558 line:80%
That's not true.

00:26:38.855 --> 00:26:39.856 line:80%
Is this about yesterday?

00:26:45.654 --> 00:26:46.655 line:80%
[shrill grunt]

00:26:47.614 --> 00:26:48.865 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:26:49.533 --> 00:26:50.700 line:80%
About what?

00:26:50.784 --> 00:26:51.785 line:80%
About last night.

00:26:52.702 --> 00:26:53.703 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:26:53.787 --> 00:26:54.788 line:80%
I'm fine with it.

00:26:55.914 --> 00:26:58.083 line:80%
It's not like we're kids or anything.

00:26:58.583 --> 00:26:59.960 line:80%
I mean, if the vibe is right…

00:27:00.961 --> 00:27:02.337 line:80%
Why not?

00:27:02.921 --> 00:27:05.090 line:80%
And with the vibe we had going yesterday,

00:27:05.173 --> 00:27:07.175 line:80%
even if it had been a complete stranger,

00:27:07.968 --> 00:27:10.262 line:80%
anyone would've done the same. Yeah…

00:27:15.350 --> 00:27:16.393 line:80%
A complete stranger…

00:27:18.353 --> 00:27:19.354 line:80%
Pardon?

00:27:19.438 --> 00:27:20.772 line:80%
Not for me.

00:27:20.856 --> 00:27:22.649 line:80%
[♪ gentle music plays]

00:27:24.568 --> 00:27:25.569 line:80%
What?

00:27:27.028 --> 00:27:28.113 line:80%
What does that mean?

00:27:29.197 --> 00:27:32.033 line:80%
I didn't do it just because
I was caught up in the moment.

00:27:35.704 --> 00:27:36.705 line:80%
I did it…

00:27:39.166 --> 00:27:40.584 line:80%
because it's you.

00:27:55.307 --> 00:27:57.184 line:80%
The Grand Prince is perturbed?

00:27:57.726 --> 00:27:58.852 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:27:58.935 --> 00:28:01.188 line:80%
Ms. Seong was by earlier in the day.

00:28:01.688 --> 00:28:03.523 line:80%
He has been a bit agitated ever since.

00:28:07.235 --> 00:28:10.447 line:80%
The date has been set,
yet he remains agitated…

00:28:14.743 --> 00:28:16.536 line:80%
I shall go for a walk with him.

00:28:23.627 --> 00:28:25.670 line:80%
Did something happen to upset you?

00:28:30.634 --> 00:28:32.177 line:80%
You appear troubled.

00:28:34.346 --> 00:28:37.140 line:80%
Could you be upset
about what happened yesterday evening?

00:28:39.017 --> 00:28:40.101 line:80%
Of course not.

00:28:41.811 --> 00:28:42.812 line:80%
Then,

00:28:44.064 --> 00:28:46.525 line:80%
did you have an argument with Ms. Seong?

00:28:48.985 --> 00:28:50.695 line:80%
It seems you wish that to be so.

00:28:54.074 --> 00:28:55.867 line:80%
I am merely worried.

00:28:56.910 --> 00:28:59.371 line:80%
You two come from different worlds.

00:29:00.038 --> 00:29:02.249 line:80%
Perfect accord cannot be easily attained.

00:29:07.212 --> 00:29:08.213 line:80%
And you?

00:29:09.548 --> 00:29:11.007 line:80%
Did you attain accord?

00:29:13.593 --> 00:29:14.844 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:29:14.928 --> 00:29:16.096 line:80%
You and my brother

00:29:17.013 --> 00:29:19.224 line:80%
grew up in the same world.

00:29:23.395 --> 00:29:24.396 line:80%
Did you two…

00:29:26.523 --> 00:29:27.774 line:80%
arrive at happiness?

00:29:32.487 --> 00:29:34.364 line:80%
How can I go by myself?

00:29:35.824 --> 00:29:37.617 line:80%
They are expecting both of us.

00:29:37.701 --> 00:29:39.035 line:80%
What would you have me do?

00:29:42.122 --> 00:29:43.123 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:29:48.837 --> 00:29:50.171 line:80%
[sighs]

00:29:51.590 --> 00:29:53.049 line:80%
Has my brother run off again?

00:29:58.263 --> 00:29:59.264 line:80%
[clicks tongue]

00:29:59.347 --> 00:30:00.557 line:80%
I shall accompany you.

00:30:02.434 --> 00:30:04.644 line:80%
If we say that the Crown Prince is unwell,

00:30:05.270 --> 00:30:08.231 line:80%
they would scarcely consider it
improper that I, the Grand Prince,

00:30:08.898 --> 00:30:10.275 line:80%
accompany you in his stead.

00:30:12.902 --> 00:30:14.863 line:80%
That would only prompt Father
to reprimand you.

00:30:14.946 --> 00:30:16.114 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:30:16.197 --> 00:30:18.533 line:80%
I'm reprimanded every day anyway.

00:30:20.327 --> 00:30:21.369 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:30:22.120 --> 00:30:23.288 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:30:38.595 --> 00:30:40.388 line:80%
Is there any place

00:30:41.556 --> 00:30:43.767 line:80%
for happiness in a royal union?

00:31:01.951 --> 00:31:02.952 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>I did it</i>

00:31:04.079 --> 00:31:05.288 line:80%
because it's you.

00:31:08.583 --> 00:31:10.043 line:80%
[sighs]

00:31:24.683 --> 00:31:28.186 line:80%
PRINCE

00:31:30.855 --> 00:31:31.856 line:80%
No.

00:31:32.357 --> 00:31:33.983 line:80%
So what?

00:31:34.067 --> 00:31:35.443 line:80%
Should we just date a little

00:31:36.486 --> 00:31:38.071 line:80%
since we're going to divorce anyway?

00:31:40.824 --> 00:31:41.825 line:80%
[in English] Nope.

00:31:53.753 --> 00:31:54.796 line:80%
[sighs]

00:32:05.348 --> 00:32:07.809 line:80%
MARRIAGE CONTRACT

00:32:10.562 --> 00:32:13.606 line:80%
4. DIVORCE WITHIN THREE YEARS
AT THE LATEST

00:32:31.750 --> 00:32:33.334 line:80%
[♪ dramatic music plays]

00:32:33.418 --> 00:32:35.587 line:80%
[screaming, clamoring]

00:32:37.380 --> 00:32:38.757 line:80%
[Im] You must hurry.

00:32:52.854 --> 00:32:54.647 line:80%
[Yun breathing shakily]

00:33:04.616 --> 00:33:06.409 line:80%
[in Korean] Why are you in such a state?

00:33:11.664 --> 00:33:13.458 line:80%
Please get up, Your Majesty.

00:33:20.256 --> 00:33:21.257 line:80%
Your Majesty?

00:33:28.848 --> 00:33:29.849 line:80%
The press

00:33:31.017 --> 00:33:33.812 line:80%
will soon spread the news
of His Majesty's tragedy.

00:33:35.188 --> 00:33:38.608 line:80%
You must secure
the Crown Prince's accession.

00:33:38.691 --> 00:33:40.944 line:80%
His Majesty had abandoned
the Crown Prince.

00:33:45.406 --> 00:33:47.325 line:80%
He wished to depose the Crown Prince…

00:33:50.787 --> 00:33:53.248 line:80%
and abdicate
in favor of Grand Prince I-AN.

00:33:54.415 --> 00:33:55.416 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:33:55.500 --> 00:33:57.961 line:80%
He even drew up a royal edict!

00:33:58.044 --> 00:33:59.838 line:80%
[breathing shakily]

00:34:07.762 --> 00:34:08.805 line:80%
I am certain…

00:34:12.183 --> 00:34:13.852 line:80%
His Majesty will understand me.

00:34:17.438 --> 00:34:19.357 line:80%
This was all for the Crown Prince's sake.

00:34:22.694 --> 00:34:23.695 line:80%
What in the world

00:34:25.113 --> 00:34:26.990 line:80%
have you done?

00:34:29.868 --> 00:34:30.869 line:80%
I…

00:34:36.583 --> 00:34:38.835 line:80%
I burned it all to the ground.

00:34:55.018 --> 00:34:56.019 line:80%
[sighs]

00:35:18.917 --> 00:35:20.460 line:80%
[safe beeps]

00:35:31.054 --> 00:35:34.057 line:80%
[♪ dramatic music plays]

00:35:51.407 --> 00:35:53.993 line:80%
AS SUCH, I INTEND TO ABDICATE

00:35:54.077 --> 00:35:56.746 line:80%
AND BE SUCCEEDED
BY GRAND PRINCE I-AN

00:35:56.829 --> 00:35:58.831 line:80%
[♪ epic music playing]

00:36:09.425 --> 00:36:12.637 line:80%
"I am most pleased to see you again,
Your Royal Highness." And then…

00:36:12.720 --> 00:36:14.430 line:80%
"It is my great honor."

00:36:15.306 --> 00:36:16.933 line:80%
-Damn it…
-Babe.

00:36:17.016 --> 00:36:18.601 line:80%
Did you not dry your hair?

00:36:18.685 --> 00:36:21.479 line:80%
I tried doing it like His Royal Highness.
Do you not like it?

00:36:21.562 --> 00:36:24.440 line:80%
Why would you copy his style?

00:36:24.524 --> 00:36:27.110 line:80%
Too many feelers? I just thought…

00:36:27.193 --> 00:36:29.904 line:80%
You're so much more handsome than him!

00:36:30.405 --> 00:36:31.823 line:80%
-Really?
-Who does Taeju belong to?

00:36:31.906 --> 00:36:34.325 line:80%
To Dayeong. Ah…

00:36:35.201 --> 00:36:37.495 line:80%
-Stop it. Come on.
-Why isn't Father coming down?

00:36:37.578 --> 00:36:39.372 line:80%
[clears throat, inhales sharply]

00:36:39.455 --> 00:36:42.041 line:80%
But what if Father
does a repeat of yesterday?

00:36:42.125 --> 00:36:43.292 line:80%
He wouldn't.

00:36:43.376 --> 00:36:45.044 line:80%
Father? Father!

00:36:45.128 --> 00:36:46.587 line:80%
I can hear you perfectly fine.

00:36:46.671 --> 00:36:48.006 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:36:48.089 --> 00:36:49.841 line:80%
Father. [chuckles]

00:36:51.092 --> 00:36:54.178 line:80%
You should lighten up a little.
We should be celebrating today.

00:36:54.262 --> 00:36:56.014 line:80%
-[in English] Smile.
-[in Korean] That's right.

00:36:56.097 --> 00:36:58.391 line:80%
You can hate your own kid,
but you shouldn't hate your son-in-law.

00:36:58.474 --> 00:37:00.184 line:80%
Especially, when he's Grand Prince I-AN.

00:37:00.268 --> 00:37:01.269 line:80%
Just look at me.

00:37:01.352 --> 00:37:04.731 line:80%
After falling for Dayeong,
I bow down to her father like it's my job.

00:37:04.814 --> 00:37:06.941 line:80%
Do you see how Grand Prince I-AN
is wasting no time?

00:37:07.025 --> 00:37:08.860 line:80%
He must be beyond smitten
with her too. I swear--

00:37:08.943 --> 00:37:10.528 line:80%
That's enough of that nonsense.

00:37:16.576 --> 00:37:17.577 line:80%
[huffs]

00:37:35.470 --> 00:37:38.097 line:80%
[Hyeon] If I could just have
your attention for a moment.

00:37:38.181 --> 00:37:41.601 line:80%
Once we arrive, there might be a bit
of a crowd waiting to see you two.

00:37:41.684 --> 00:37:44.437 line:80%
Please remember to smile
when you step out.

00:37:44.520 --> 00:37:47.815 line:80%
Ms. Seong, you can just follow
the Grand Prince's lead and wave.

00:37:53.821 --> 00:37:54.822 line:80%
And the Royal Guard?

00:37:54.906 --> 00:37:57.492 line:80%
We should be fine.
We dispatched double the normal amount.

00:37:58.576 --> 00:37:59.786 line:80%
-What about…
-What about…

00:38:06.042 --> 00:38:08.002 line:80%
Do we have an end time?

00:38:08.086 --> 00:38:10.713 line:80%
There's no rush.
You should just enjoy your meal,

00:38:10.797 --> 00:38:13.007 line:80%
but at the minimum,
we're thinking four hours…

00:38:13.091 --> 00:38:14.133 line:80%
Four hours?

00:38:14.217 --> 00:38:15.718 line:80%
[Hyeon] Well, you see,

00:38:15.802 --> 00:38:18.346 line:80%
if you leave too early,
it may be seen as discourteous.

00:38:18.429 --> 00:38:21.933 line:80%
If too late, the other members
of the royal family will grow jealous.

00:38:22.016 --> 00:38:25.186 line:80%
[chuckles] I'd appreciate it if you
kept these things in mind.

00:38:42.120 --> 00:38:43.996 line:80%
Please forgive the delayed greetings.

00:38:45.331 --> 00:38:46.332 line:80%
Father.

00:38:48.876 --> 00:38:52.588 line:80%
[clears throat] Well,
we are very honored to host you,

00:38:52.672 --> 00:38:54.465 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:38:55.049 --> 00:38:57.844 line:80%
My dear younger sister is not perforated.
I mean, not perfect.

00:38:57.927 --> 00:39:00.638 line:80%
We hope she does not prove an impediment.

00:39:01.389 --> 00:39:02.515 line:80%
-And…
-[clears throat]

00:39:04.517 --> 00:39:06.018 line:80%
I, Hyeonguk of the Seong Family,

00:39:06.644 --> 00:39:08.646 line:80%
offer you my greetings,
Your Royal Highness.

00:39:13.151 --> 00:39:14.360 line:80%
This is my son.

00:39:14.443 --> 00:39:16.696 line:80%
I'm the Senior Managing Director
of Castle Group

00:39:16.779 --> 00:39:18.531 line:80%
and his soon-to-be successor…

00:39:19.866 --> 00:39:20.908 line:80%
Yes, right.

00:39:21.659 --> 00:39:23.786 line:80%
I remember, Brother.

00:39:25.413 --> 00:39:27.415 line:80%
[chuckles] Yes, I see.

00:39:27.498 --> 00:39:29.292 line:80%
Uh… [chuckles]

00:39:29.375 --> 00:39:30.585 line:80%
"Brother"? Insane.

00:39:30.668 --> 00:39:32.378 line:80%
You mean, "Your Royal Highness."

00:39:32.962 --> 00:39:37.884 line:80%
[chuckles] Yes, right. He already… Yeah.

00:39:37.967 --> 00:39:40.094 line:80%
[both chuckle]

00:39:42.180 --> 00:39:43.181 line:80%
[sighs]

00:39:48.853 --> 00:39:51.439 line:80%
I mean, I know it's just an…

00:39:53.774 --> 00:39:55.109 line:80%
just an act and all,

00:39:55.193 --> 00:39:57.486 line:80%
but they're so stiff
around each other, aren't they?

00:39:57.570 --> 00:39:59.655 line:80%
I'm so scared they're going to get caught.

00:39:59.739 --> 00:40:00.990 line:80%
I hear you.

00:40:01.073 --> 00:40:04.285 line:80%
I heard it was super awkward
during the health assessment yesterday.

00:40:04.368 --> 00:40:06.787 line:80%
I mean, can you imagine
how tense she must've been?

00:40:06.871 --> 00:40:09.916 line:80%
To make her heart pound like that?

00:40:09.999 --> 00:40:11.042 line:80%
But…

00:40:12.251 --> 00:40:14.378 line:80%
-Don't you think it's excessive?
-My thoughts exactly.

00:40:14.462 --> 00:40:16.672 line:80%
-Maybe they're falling for each other.
-What?

00:40:16.756 --> 00:40:19.592 line:80%
I mean, they actually look like
they just started dating.

00:40:20.843 --> 00:40:22.011 line:80%
Just started dating…

00:40:23.054 --> 00:40:24.263 line:80%
Oh?

00:40:24.347 --> 00:40:26.057 line:80%
[phone chimes]

00:40:27.558 --> 00:40:29.393 line:80%
[gasps] I need to go.

00:40:29.477 --> 00:40:30.645 line:80%
I'll come with you.

00:40:31.145 --> 00:40:33.773 line:80%
No, you should finish all this first.

00:40:35.024 --> 00:40:36.025 line:80%
I'm off.

00:40:36.859 --> 00:40:38.444 line:80%
Okay. See you later.

00:40:41.697 --> 00:40:42.990 line:80%
[sighs]

00:40:51.499 --> 00:40:54.502 line:80%
[♪ romantic music plays]

00:41:12.853 --> 00:41:14.105 line:80%
[Taeju] Yes, thanks.

00:41:14.814 --> 00:41:16.565 line:80%
[clears throat] Thank you.

00:41:16.649 --> 00:41:19.193 line:80%
I'm actually the CEO
of Castle Hotel as well.

00:41:19.277 --> 00:41:22.405 line:80%
I had some of our chefs come by
to cook this. How is it?

00:41:22.488 --> 00:41:24.490 line:80%
You're not the CEO yet.

00:41:24.573 --> 00:41:26.617 line:80%
That handover hasn't happened yet.

00:41:26.701 --> 00:41:28.160 line:80%
Must you bring that up now?

00:41:28.703 --> 00:41:30.705 line:80%
[stammers] It's almost done.

00:41:31.998 --> 00:41:33.874 line:80%
It's all very good, Brother.

00:41:33.958 --> 00:41:35.209 line:80%
Oh… [chuckles]

00:41:35.293 --> 00:41:36.294 line:80%
Is it?

00:41:36.836 --> 00:41:38.921 line:80%
I'm so glad.

00:41:39.005 --> 00:41:43.843 line:80%
[inhales sharply]
Can I ask when you two started dating?

00:41:44.969 --> 00:41:45.970 line:80%
-Pardon?
-Well, you see,

00:41:46.053 --> 00:41:48.597 line:80%
she used to have terrible taste in men.

00:41:48.681 --> 00:41:51.350 line:80%
What do they call it?
You know, the ones you carry around.

00:41:51.434 --> 00:41:53.561 line:80%
Who cares about that now?

00:41:53.644 --> 00:41:55.396 line:80%
Oh, right. Trophy boys.

00:41:55.479 --> 00:41:58.691 line:80%
She used to be really into trophy boys.
They were always so skinny.

00:41:58.774 --> 00:42:00.985 line:80%
But somehow, she landed
a really solid husband.

00:42:01.068 --> 00:42:03.029 line:80%
-[smacks table]
-Seong…

00:42:03.654 --> 00:42:04.655 line:80%
Dear brother.

00:42:05.948 --> 00:42:07.742 line:80%
Relax. It's a compliment.

00:42:07.825 --> 00:42:09.118 line:80%
Just look at Our Royal Highness.

00:42:09.201 --> 00:42:12.246 line:80%
He's so tall. Almost as tall
as the doorframe. And his shoulders…

00:42:12.330 --> 00:42:14.332 line:80%
Yeah, they're almost
as broad as this table.

00:42:14.415 --> 00:42:16.959 line:80%
-That's a real man for you…
-[chuckles]

00:42:17.043 --> 00:42:21.213 line:80%
He's just trying to say
that you make a really nice couple.

00:42:21.297 --> 00:42:22.423 line:80%
Yeah, that's right.

00:42:23.049 --> 00:42:24.383 line:80%
-Stop drinking.
-Okay.

00:42:25.551 --> 00:42:27.845 line:80%
-Yeah, a nice couple. Mmm…
-[sighs]

00:42:27.928 --> 00:42:29.513 line:80%
[Hyeonguk] Please…

00:42:30.598 --> 00:42:32.141 line:80%
cherish her.

00:42:35.978 --> 00:42:38.564 line:80%
She spent her whole life
thinking highly of herself,

00:42:38.647 --> 00:42:39.648 line:80%
so I had hoped

00:42:41.108 --> 00:42:43.069 line:80%
she'd end up with someone
a bit beneath her.

00:42:43.152 --> 00:42:46.238 line:80%
I cannot help but be concerned
about her marrying into the royal family.

00:42:46.322 --> 00:42:48.824 line:80%
I will do my best to make sure
you have nothing to worry--

00:42:48.908 --> 00:42:51.118 line:80%
If that was all it took,
I would not worry.

00:42:52.078 --> 00:42:54.789 line:80%
[♪ tense music plays]

00:42:59.210 --> 00:43:00.211 line:80%
That place is known

00:43:01.003 --> 00:43:03.506 line:80%
for its troubles and tragedies, is it not?

00:43:12.098 --> 00:43:14.141 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:43:16.394 --> 00:43:17.395 line:80%
That doesn't

00:43:18.020 --> 00:43:19.021 line:80%
quite hold up, does it?

00:43:21.023 --> 00:43:22.608 line:80%
Who are you trying to kid?

00:43:24.860 --> 00:43:26.862 line:80%
Am I wrong? [sighs]

00:43:26.946 --> 00:43:29.281 line:80%
Where was that ever-worried father

00:43:29.365 --> 00:43:32.451 line:80%
when I got into that car accident?

00:43:34.328 --> 00:43:35.913 line:80%
It just doesn't add up, does it?

00:43:37.540 --> 00:43:40.334 line:80%
As you can see, she is still a child.

00:43:41.669 --> 00:43:43.337 line:80%
-She has her shortcomings--
-[smacks table]

00:43:43.421 --> 00:43:45.423 line:80%
That's enough small talk, isn't it?

00:43:46.132 --> 00:43:47.925 line:80%
Don't you have a wedding gift for us?

00:43:48.634 --> 00:43:50.344 line:80%
I mean, when Taeju got married,

00:43:51.011 --> 00:43:54.181 line:80%
you gave Dayeong's family
company shares and even a building.

00:43:54.265 --> 00:43:55.474 line:80%
All on a silver platter.

00:43:58.602 --> 00:44:01.105 line:80%
[coughs]

00:44:01.814 --> 00:44:03.899 line:80%
Your one and only daughter
is getting married.

00:44:05.067 --> 00:44:06.610 line:80%
Surely, you must have something.

00:44:08.654 --> 00:44:09.697 line:80%
How about

00:44:10.739 --> 00:44:12.575 line:80%
a generous donation to the crown?

00:44:12.658 --> 00:44:13.742 line:80%
[Taeju] Hey.

00:44:14.326 --> 00:44:16.245 line:80%
You're making
His Royal Highness uncomfortable.

00:44:17.496 --> 00:44:18.497 line:80%
[sighs]

00:44:19.999 --> 00:44:22.960 line:80%
You can finish this meal without me.

00:44:23.043 --> 00:44:24.920 line:80%
I thought I could practice restraint…

00:44:25.921 --> 00:44:27.423 line:80%
[sucks teeth, inhales sharply]

00:44:27.506 --> 00:44:28.632 line:80%
…but it's just too hard.

00:44:38.309 --> 00:44:39.768 line:80%
-[sighs]
-[Taeju] Hmm…

00:44:44.440 --> 00:44:45.774 line:80%
Let me check on her.

00:45:03.918 --> 00:45:05.002 line:80%
[sighs]

00:45:13.427 --> 00:45:14.428 line:80%
Seong Huiju.

00:45:17.932 --> 00:45:18.933 line:80%
[sighs]

00:45:23.229 --> 00:45:26.065 line:80%
[Huiju breathing slowly, deeply]

00:45:40.663 --> 00:45:42.164 line:80%
Just let me be for a second.

00:45:42.998 --> 00:45:45.626 line:80%
I'll come back down
once my anger subsides a bit.

00:45:52.800 --> 00:45:54.009 line:80%
[I-AN grunts, sighs]

00:45:58.806 --> 00:45:59.807 line:80%
What?

00:46:01.684 --> 00:46:04.812 line:80%
Are you having second thoughts?
Because my family is such a hot mess?

00:46:08.732 --> 00:46:10.025 line:80%
You must have a bad memory.

00:46:13.362 --> 00:46:15.197 line:80%
If you remembered
what Queen Mother said to me,

00:46:15.906 --> 00:46:17.324 line:80%
there's no way you'd say that.

00:46:21.745 --> 00:46:22.746 line:80%
That's true.

00:46:25.874 --> 00:46:28.502 line:80%
Doesn't it seem like your father likes me?

00:46:32.089 --> 00:46:33.924 line:80%
-You believed that?
-Should I not?

00:46:34.550 --> 00:46:37.428 line:80%
That doting, concerned father bit
is all an act.

00:46:38.304 --> 00:46:41.056 line:80%
The result of him running
the numbers and sizing up

00:46:41.974 --> 00:46:43.642 line:80%
what he could gain by using you.

00:46:55.988 --> 00:46:56.989 line:80%
Who cares?

00:46:58.157 --> 00:46:59.241 line:80%
As long as I'm genuine.

00:47:00.451 --> 00:47:03.120 line:80%
[♪ tender song playing]

00:47:03.203 --> 00:47:05.164 line:80%
I have a great deal that you do not,

00:47:06.040 --> 00:47:07.249 line:80%
and if you ask for it,

00:47:08.667 --> 00:47:10.252 line:80%
I fully intend to provide it.

00:47:25.517 --> 00:47:26.518 line:80%
By chance,

00:47:28.187 --> 00:47:29.855 line:80%
do you have feelings for me?

00:47:31.565 --> 00:47:33.942 line:80%
-All of a sudden?
-Then was I

00:47:35.027 --> 00:47:37.946 line:80%
your first… or something?

00:47:39.031 --> 00:47:40.115 line:80%
What?

00:47:40.199 --> 00:47:41.784 line:80%
I mean… [sucks teeth]

00:47:42.868 --> 00:47:46.705 line:80%
It's true. I can be quite a femme fatale.

00:47:48.374 --> 00:47:49.583 line:80%
But still,

00:47:51.043 --> 00:47:53.003 line:80%
your eyes are sparkling a little too much.

00:48:00.427 --> 00:48:01.553 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:48:02.179 --> 00:48:03.430 line:80%
[laughs]

00:48:09.395 --> 00:48:10.521 line:80%
I do like you.

00:48:12.022 --> 00:48:13.148 line:80%
And it's my first time.

00:48:18.278 --> 00:48:20.072 line:80%
Restraint always followed desire.

00:48:22.491 --> 00:48:23.784 line:80%
But it's not easy this time.

00:48:29.248 --> 00:48:31.458 line:80%
What? Having second thoughts?

00:48:33.043 --> 00:48:34.628 line:80%
Worried I won't divorce you?

00:48:37.631 --> 00:48:38.632 line:80%
You won't?

00:48:44.471 --> 00:48:45.472 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:48:46.765 --> 00:48:48.475 line:80%
I don't want to keep you bound to me.

00:48:53.605 --> 00:48:55.023 line:80%
You should just accept it all.

00:48:56.608 --> 00:48:58.152 line:80%
Whether it be money, honor,

00:48:59.862 --> 00:49:00.946 line:80%
or my heart…

00:49:01.029 --> 00:49:02.948 line:80%
[♪ song continuing]

00:49:16.837 --> 00:49:18.756 line:80%
I've always had more money than you.

00:49:20.132 --> 00:49:21.175 line:80%
Always?

00:49:21.258 --> 00:49:22.676 line:80%
Always have.

00:49:22.760 --> 00:49:24.011 line:80%
-"Always have"?
-Always will.

00:49:26.305 --> 00:49:27.806 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:49:44.656 --> 00:49:46.658 line:80%
[♪ song continuing]

00:50:18.899 --> 00:50:20.859 line:80%
[phone buzzing]

00:50:25.197 --> 00:50:26.573 line:80%
JEONGWOO

00:50:30.369 --> 00:50:31.453 line:80%
What? Pick it up.

00:50:37.626 --> 00:50:38.961 line:80%
Hey, Jeongwoo.

00:50:39.753 --> 00:50:42.589 line:80%
Yeah, it's over. We're heading back
to the private residence.

00:50:45.008 --> 00:50:47.261 line:80%
Yeah, he's right next to me.

00:50:47.886 --> 00:50:49.137 line:80%
Sure. Hold on.

00:50:53.642 --> 00:50:55.686 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] <i>Your Royal Highness,</i>
<i>did it go well?</i>

00:50:55.769 --> 00:50:56.895 line:80%
Yeah.

00:50:56.979 --> 00:50:59.356 line:80%
My father-in-law loves me.

00:50:59.439 --> 00:51:01.108 line:80%
<i>Really?</i> [chuckles]

00:51:01.900 --> 00:51:03.610 line:80%
<i>I guess you didn't fight</i>
<i>with your father today.</i>

00:51:03.694 --> 00:51:06.405 line:80%
Do you think I just go around
starting fights everywhere?

00:51:06.488 --> 00:51:07.739 line:80%
[Jeongwoo chuckles]

00:51:07.823 --> 00:51:09.575 line:80%
<i>And Taeju? Did he behave?</i>

00:51:14.413 --> 00:51:15.414 line:80%
He was whatever.

00:51:16.415 --> 00:51:20.043 line:80%
I still can't tell if handing over
the reins to him was a good idea.

00:51:21.712 --> 00:51:22.754 line:80%
Yeah. [chuckles]

00:51:24.673 --> 00:51:25.757 line:80%
I know, right?

00:51:27.134 --> 00:51:29.177 line:80%
What about you? Are you done with work?

00:51:39.313 --> 00:51:40.772 line:80%
I'll see you on our wedding day.

00:51:46.820 --> 00:51:48.030 line:80%
I'm sad about leaving too.

00:51:59.374 --> 00:52:00.584 line:80%
[car door opens]

00:52:04.755 --> 00:52:05.923 line:80%
[car door shuts]

00:52:13.138 --> 00:52:14.473 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:52:20.145 --> 00:52:21.313 line:80%
How did it go?

00:52:21.396 --> 00:52:22.606 line:80%
Did the chairman like him?

00:52:22.689 --> 00:52:27.277 line:80%
-Of course, he did. How could he not?
-Earlier, His Royal Highness was like,

00:52:27.361 --> 00:52:28.487 line:80%
"I'm sad about leaving too."

00:52:29.655 --> 00:52:31.531 line:80%
-He said that before he left.
-[giggling]

00:52:31.615 --> 00:52:33.408 line:80%
Was His Royal Highness nervous?
Did he do well?

00:52:33.492 --> 00:52:35.702 line:80%
Have you been waiting for me
to ask about that?

00:52:36.370 --> 00:52:38.205 line:80%
-Yes.
-They couldn't even eat.

00:52:38.288 --> 00:52:39.456 line:80%
They were all so nervous.

00:52:39.539 --> 00:52:41.541 line:80%
-Still?
-Yes.

00:52:41.625 --> 00:52:43.001 line:80%
[sighs, scoffs]

00:52:43.085 --> 00:52:45.045 line:80%
I know it's late,

00:52:46.046 --> 00:52:47.047 line:80%
but should we grab a bite?

00:52:47.130 --> 00:52:49.007 line:80%
-Yes.
-Yes please!

00:52:49.091 --> 00:52:50.550 line:80%
What about that new place?

00:52:50.634 --> 00:52:52.803 line:80%
You said that place was delicious.

00:52:52.886 --> 00:52:55.097 line:80%
-Where is this place?
-Yeah, we should go there.

00:53:00.227 --> 00:53:01.561 line:80%
[server] Enjoy.

00:53:01.645 --> 00:53:04.106 line:80%
Thank you. All right, then.

00:53:04.189 --> 00:53:05.607 line:80%
Eat up now.

00:53:05.691 --> 00:53:07.442 line:80%
It'll all be

00:53:08.110 --> 00:53:09.361 line:80%
my treat tonight.

00:53:09.444 --> 00:53:11.947 line:80%
-Thank you.
-Thank you so much.

00:53:14.032 --> 00:53:15.701 line:80%
[exclaims]

00:53:15.784 --> 00:53:17.119 line:80%
Mmm!

00:53:17.202 --> 00:53:18.704 line:80%
-It's so good.
-[chuckles]

00:53:18.787 --> 00:53:20.664 line:80%
Your Ladyship, you should have some too.

00:53:20.747 --> 00:53:21.748 line:80%
Poor thing.

00:53:21.832 --> 00:53:24.376 line:80%
You must've been too nervous to eat.

00:53:25.836 --> 00:53:28.797 line:80%
You must be a ball of nerves
with the wedding approaching.

00:53:28.880 --> 00:53:33.051 line:80%
Come on, a lot of people go on diets
before their wedding.

00:53:33.135 --> 00:53:34.219 line:80%
As if.

00:53:34.302 --> 00:53:38.098 line:80%
She's already light as a feather.
Why would she go on a diet?

00:53:38.181 --> 00:53:41.977 line:80%
[groans] I'm taking
a night off from that diet.

00:53:42.060 --> 00:53:43.103 line:80%
-Eat up.
-Excellent.

00:53:45.522 --> 00:53:46.523 line:80%
Mmm…

00:53:47.232 --> 00:53:48.233 line:80%
Mmm!

00:53:48.316 --> 00:53:52.279 line:80%
We've been meaning to throw you
a little bridal shower.

00:53:52.362 --> 00:53:54.197 line:80%
Maybe we can pick up a cake later?

00:53:54.281 --> 00:53:56.950 line:80%
[Yeongmun] Her Ladyship must be tired.
Just eat up.

00:53:59.995 --> 00:54:01.371 line:80%
Areum, why aren't you eating?

00:54:01.455 --> 00:54:03.331 line:80%
I thought you liked this place.

00:54:03.415 --> 00:54:06.501 line:80%
Ah… I'm just taking my time.
You should eat up too.

00:54:08.587 --> 00:54:10.005 line:80%
-Hmm…
-Here, eat this.

00:54:12.799 --> 00:54:13.884 line:80%
It's good.

00:54:14.801 --> 00:54:16.803 line:80%
[♪ dramatic music plays]

00:54:27.064 --> 00:54:28.899 line:80%
This is the Treasury's revised proposal.

00:54:28.982 --> 00:54:30.525 line:80%
Please take a look.

00:54:32.736 --> 00:54:33.820 line:80%
[phone rings]

00:54:35.655 --> 00:54:38.158 line:80%
[assistant] <i>Sir,</i>
<i>His Royal Highness is here for you.</i>

00:54:40.077 --> 00:54:41.411 line:80%
He is?

00:54:41.495 --> 00:54:43.080 line:80%
It's not on your schedule.

00:54:52.464 --> 00:54:53.465 line:80%
You busy?

00:55:04.267 --> 00:55:05.352 line:80%
Can I get you anything?

00:55:07.395 --> 00:55:08.605 line:80%
I like Seong Huiju.

00:55:12.150 --> 00:55:13.527 line:80%
I thought you should know.

00:55:15.946 --> 00:55:17.322 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:55:19.825 --> 00:55:20.909 line:80%
And does my knowing that

00:55:21.576 --> 00:55:22.577 line:80%
change anything?

00:55:23.829 --> 00:55:24.871 line:80%
It'll make sure

00:55:26.331 --> 00:55:27.666 line:80%
you mind your conduct.

00:55:36.925 --> 00:55:38.260 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:55:40.178 --> 00:55:42.305 line:80%
Does Huiju know too?

00:55:46.810 --> 00:55:48.687 line:80%
I'm talking about myself right now.

00:55:49.938 --> 00:55:50.981 line:80%
Not her.

00:55:51.523 --> 00:55:52.774 line:80%
Don't make…

00:55:54.985 --> 00:55:56.444 line:80%
things difficult for Huiju.

00:55:57.529 --> 00:55:58.530 line:80%
What?

00:55:58.613 --> 00:56:00.198 line:80%
That's not

00:56:01.575 --> 00:56:02.784 line:80%
what she wants from you.

00:56:19.551 --> 00:56:20.552 line:80%
Where's Seong Huiju?

00:56:20.635 --> 00:56:23.096 line:80%
Ah… She went into a board meeting
two hours ago.

00:56:23.180 --> 00:56:24.598 line:80%
She should be done by now.

00:56:26.099 --> 00:56:27.475 line:80%
She's probably in transit now.

00:56:27.559 --> 00:56:30.270 line:80%
She said she was visiting an affiliate
right after the meeting.

00:56:31.229 --> 00:56:34.024 line:80%
-[sighs] She'll have no time to eat.
-Exactly.

00:56:34.107 --> 00:56:36.860 line:80%
Her shares and duties must be transferred
before the wedding.

00:56:36.943 --> 00:56:39.070 line:80%
She has so much on her plate.

00:56:39.154 --> 00:56:42.115 line:80%
Meaning poor Ms. Do
must also be suffering…

00:56:44.743 --> 00:56:45.952 line:80%
Thanks for your hard work.

00:56:52.167 --> 00:56:54.127 line:80%
DON'T FORGET TO EAT…

00:57:00.550 --> 00:57:01.551 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:57:02.969 --> 00:57:04.638 line:80%
She's everywhere.

00:57:09.184 --> 00:57:11.811 line:80%
-Why are they taking that down?
-Pardon?

00:57:11.895 --> 00:57:13.939 line:80%
Oh, that? It needs to be taken down now.

00:57:14.022 --> 00:57:16.399 line:80%
Her Royal Highness cannot engage
in personal promotion.

00:57:19.194 --> 00:57:20.278 line:80%
[sighs]

00:57:24.741 --> 00:57:27.327 line:20%
[I-AN] <i>Don't forget to eat</i>
<i>just because you're busy.</i>

00:57:27.410 --> 00:57:30.538 line:80%
<i>Why'd you pull that ad already?</i>
<i>Make money while you still can.</i>

00:57:32.207 --> 00:57:33.667 line:80%
-[Hyejeong] Ms. Seong.
-What?

00:57:38.672 --> 00:57:40.006 line:80%
-Continue.
-Yes, ma'am.

00:57:40.632 --> 00:57:42.467 line:80%
Next, we are developing plans

00:57:42.550 --> 00:57:44.761 line:80%
for local marketing campaigns
and influencer partnerships,

00:57:44.844 --> 00:57:47.430 line:80%
along with a training program
for the new product launch.

00:57:47.514 --> 00:57:49.849 line:80%
We're in the final review stage
of the contracts.

00:57:50.850 --> 00:57:53.019 line:80%
Okay. Sounds good.

00:57:53.103 --> 00:57:54.104 line:80%
[giggles]

00:57:55.689 --> 00:57:58.400 line:80%
[♪ whimsical music plays]

00:58:04.114 --> 00:58:05.115 line:80%
<i>Your Royal Highness.</i>

00:58:06.116 --> 00:58:08.785 line:80%
The ceremonial robe has arrived
from the Royal Tailor Institution.

00:58:25.969 --> 00:58:27.304 line:80%
Are you that delighted?

00:58:30.015 --> 00:58:31.057 line:80%
No.

00:58:31.975 --> 00:58:33.685 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:58:33.768 --> 00:58:35.395 line:80%
-Where's Huiju?
-Ms. Seong is--

00:58:35.478 --> 00:58:36.521 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:58:37.188 --> 00:58:40.317 line:80%
You must now observe
the proper forms of address.

00:58:42.068 --> 00:58:43.069 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:58:44.529 --> 00:58:47.282 line:80%
Where… is my wife?

00:58:51.411 --> 00:58:52.579 line:80%
What is she doing?

00:59:02.756 --> 00:59:06.259 line:80%
Your Ladyship!

00:59:11.389 --> 00:59:12.390 line:80%
[Hyejeong] Right.

00:59:15.393 --> 00:59:16.394 line:80%
Okay.

00:59:16.478 --> 00:59:18.980 line:80%
So once you put on
that crimson ceremonial robe…

00:59:19.064 --> 00:59:22.400 line:80%
-Crimson?
-Your eyeliner will smudge.

00:59:23.568 --> 00:59:26.821 line:80%
I finally get to wear red
and walk into the palace?

00:59:26.905 --> 00:59:28.615 line:80%
Here. The Ministry of Rites…

00:59:28.698 --> 00:59:29.949 line:80%
[Dayeong] Huiju!

00:59:30.909 --> 00:59:32.160 line:80%
My goodness.

00:59:32.660 --> 00:59:35.663 line:80%
Why are you here so early?

00:59:36.539 --> 00:59:41.211 line:80%
You and your assistant have little regard
for court or noble etiquette.

00:59:41.294 --> 00:59:44.339 line:80%
As a lady of a noble house,
I'll have to review everything myself.

00:59:45.924 --> 00:59:46.925 line:80%
[sighs]

00:59:54.641 --> 00:59:56.518 line:80%
Mmm… Not bad.

00:59:59.062 --> 01:00:01.898 line:80%
-Have her wedding shoes arrived?
-Yes, they have!

01:00:09.364 --> 01:00:11.074 line:80%
-My goodness!
-Oh, my!

01:00:11.157 --> 01:00:13.618 line:80%
[giggles] This is how
you protect your heels.

01:00:13.701 --> 01:00:15.453 line:80%
You'll be wearing them all day.

01:00:15.537 --> 01:00:17.705 line:80%
I see. That makes sense.

01:00:18.331 --> 01:00:20.041 line:80%
-[phone buzzes]
-Hmm?

01:00:22.919 --> 01:00:23.920 line:80%
Hey, Jeongwoo.

01:00:24.504 --> 01:00:25.755 line:80%
Are preparations going well?

01:00:26.339 --> 01:00:27.882 line:80%
You sure you don't want to call it off?

01:00:27.966 --> 01:00:28.967 line:80%
[scoffs]

01:00:29.050 --> 01:00:31.594 line:80%
-And if I say I do, would you help me?
-[chuckles]

01:00:35.557 --> 01:00:36.558 line:80%
Prime Minister Min.

01:00:38.184 --> 01:00:39.185 line:80%
I'll call you back.

01:00:48.403 --> 01:00:50.238 line:80%
Are you still not dressed?

01:00:52.115 --> 01:00:53.867 line:80%
Are you all right?

01:00:56.327 --> 01:00:58.288 line:80%
Why would I not be?

01:01:01.416 --> 01:01:02.417 line:80%
Then…

01:01:04.461 --> 01:01:05.628 line:80%
I shall wait.

01:01:10.383 --> 01:01:13.011 line:80%
Until the day you can
no longer restrain yourself.

01:01:27.192 --> 01:01:29.360 line:80%
Do we just wait here?

01:01:30.028 --> 01:01:33.031 line:80%
[♪ elegant music plays]

01:01:40.663 --> 01:01:42.040 line:80%
[gasps]

01:01:42.123 --> 01:01:44.042 line:80%
Huiju looks so pretty.

01:01:45.668 --> 01:01:47.212 line:80%
No, you're way prettier.

01:01:58.348 --> 01:02:00.475 line:80%
Congratulations on your nuptials.

01:02:00.558 --> 01:02:02.435 line:80%
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations.

01:02:09.984 --> 01:02:11.694 line:80%
[inhales sharply]

01:02:11.778 --> 01:02:14.989 line:80%
You're officially
the Grand Prince's wife. [giggles]

01:02:15.073 --> 01:02:17.158 line:80%
So? You like it?

01:02:20.078 --> 01:02:21.162 line:80%
[sighs]

01:02:27.502 --> 01:02:28.920 line:80%
[♪ traditional Korean music plays]

01:02:29.003 --> 01:02:30.588 line:80%
[officiant] All bow deeply!

01:02:51.859 --> 01:02:53.069 line:80%
All rise!

01:03:04.289 --> 01:03:06.165 line:80%
-[grunts]
-[gasps]

01:03:06.249 --> 01:03:07.667 line:80%
-You're okay.
-Your Ladyship.

01:03:07.750 --> 01:03:08.751 line:80%
Damn it…

01:03:09.460 --> 01:03:10.878 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:03:15.133 --> 01:03:19.470 line:80%
The bride and groom
shall exchange deep bows.

01:03:20.179 --> 01:03:22.432 line:80%
[♪ light orchestral music playing]

01:03:23.516 --> 01:03:25.852 line:80%
By sharing this wine,

01:03:26.394 --> 01:03:28.605 line:80%
you are now equals in status and soul.

01:03:30.189 --> 01:03:34.277 line:80%
I proclaim to Heaven and Earth
that you are joined as husband and wife.

01:03:37.071 --> 01:03:39.198 line:80%
[coughs]

01:03:40.950 --> 01:03:42.035 line:80%
Are you all right?

01:03:42.702 --> 01:03:43.828 line:80%
[coughs]

01:03:43.911 --> 01:03:44.912 line:80%
[strained] I'm fine.

01:03:45.496 --> 01:03:46.497 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:03:47.332 --> 01:03:52.503 line:80%
The father of the bride
shall now offer words of caution.

01:03:55.089 --> 01:03:56.883 line:80%
Show caution and reverence.

01:03:56.966 --> 01:03:59.385 line:80%
From early dawn until late at night,

01:03:59.469 --> 01:04:01.679 line:80%
let there be no deviation from command.

01:04:03.097 --> 01:04:04.098 line:80%
Yes.

01:04:04.724 --> 01:04:06.643 line:80%
I shall carry out your command faithfully.

01:04:08.353 --> 01:04:09.395 line:80%
Do not look down.

01:04:10.229 --> 01:04:11.272 line:80%
It makes you look weak.

01:04:34.629 --> 01:04:37.131 line:80%
-[cheering]
-[♪ marching music plays]

01:05:09.122 --> 01:05:10.957 line:80%
My goodness! Her Ladyship looks so…

01:05:11.040 --> 01:05:13.668 line:80%
No, I mean, Her Royal Highness. [giggles]

01:05:13.751 --> 01:05:15.712 line:80%
Her lips must be on the verge of spasming.

01:05:15.795 --> 01:05:17.255 line:80%
Just look at that perfect makeup.

01:05:17.338 --> 01:05:19.757 line:80%
Aren't you glad I used pink coral
instead of coral pink?

01:05:19.841 --> 01:05:20.842 line:80%
[Youngseon] Totally.

01:05:20.925 --> 01:05:23.344 line:80%
Just look at that massive crowd.

01:05:23.428 --> 01:05:25.638 line:80%
I don't think it was that big
for the Queen Mother.

01:05:25.722 --> 01:05:27.014 line:80%
Definitely not.

01:05:27.974 --> 01:05:31.561 line:80%
[coughs] Gosh. Why am I tearing up?

01:05:31.644 --> 01:05:34.147 line:80%
You look like your son's getting married.

01:05:35.606 --> 01:05:38.025 line:80%
Steward Kim, are you crying?

01:05:38.109 --> 01:05:39.235 line:80%
[inhales sharply]

01:05:39.819 --> 01:05:41.404 line:80%
[sighs]

01:05:41.487 --> 01:05:44.198 line:80%
Our Royal Highness is all grown up now.

01:05:45.241 --> 01:05:46.909 line:80%
-Hey, we crushed that.
-Gosh.

01:05:46.993 --> 01:05:48.119 line:80%
We crushed it!

01:06:00.506 --> 01:06:01.632 line:80%
Smile.

01:06:01.716 --> 01:06:04.635 line:80%
My jaw is about to snap
from all this smiling.

01:06:06.053 --> 01:06:09.015 line:80%
How do you do this for every single event?

01:06:10.224 --> 01:06:11.267 line:80%
Just hang in there.

01:06:12.769 --> 01:06:13.770 line:80%
We're almost there.

01:06:30.244 --> 01:06:32.580 line:80%
THE MARRIAGE PROCESSION OF
GRAND PRINCE I-AN

01:06:32.663 --> 01:06:34.499 line:80%
AND GRAND PRINCESS SEONG

01:06:34.582 --> 01:06:37.585 line:80%
[♪ melancholic music plays]

01:06:56.395 --> 01:06:58.815 line:80%
That is why I told you to veto it.

01:07:01.025 --> 01:07:02.485 line:80%
What is long suppressed

01:07:03.820 --> 01:07:05.822 line:80%
tends to erupt
in the most unexpected ways.

01:07:11.577 --> 01:07:13.579 line:80%
[camera shutters clicking]

01:07:26.050 --> 01:07:27.510 line:80%
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations.

01:07:27.593 --> 01:07:29.428 line:80%
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations.

01:07:35.059 --> 01:07:36.769 line:80%
The most sincere congratulations

01:07:36.853 --> 01:07:39.772 line:80%
to His Royal Highness
and Her Royal Highness.

01:07:45.653 --> 01:07:47.154 line:80%
Congratulations on achieving

01:07:47.738 --> 01:07:48.739 line:80%
nominal status.

01:07:52.743 --> 01:07:53.744 line:80%
[scoffs]

01:07:56.581 --> 01:07:58.666 line:80%
[♪ romantic music plays]

01:08:11.512 --> 01:08:13.139 line:80%
[Court Lady Choi] Your Majesty.

01:08:13.222 --> 01:08:15.558 line:80%
The Grand Prince
and his wife have arrived.

01:09:24.377 --> 01:09:25.878 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] Grand Prince I-AN.

01:09:26.462 --> 01:09:29.006 line:80%
On behalf of the people and the Cabinet,

01:09:29.715 --> 01:09:32.343 line:80%
I offer my most sincere congratulations
on your union.

01:09:33.469 --> 01:09:35.596 line:80%
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations.

01:09:36.180 --> 01:09:37.598 line:80%
Thank you, Prime Minister.

01:09:39.725 --> 01:09:41.060 line:80%
[sighs]

01:09:42.395 --> 01:09:43.521 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] Your Royal Highness.

01:09:44.313 --> 01:09:46.065 line:80%
On behalf of the people and the Cabinet,

01:09:46.816 --> 01:09:47.858 line:80%
I offer

01:09:48.734 --> 01:09:50.277 line:80%
my most sincere congratulations…

01:09:56.993 --> 01:09:58.077 line:80%
on your union.

01:10:01.122 --> 01:10:02.790 line:80%
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations.

01:10:03.582 --> 01:10:05.001 line:80%
Thank… [coughs]

01:10:06.836 --> 01:10:08.838 line:80%
[coughing]

01:10:11.048 --> 01:10:12.174 line:80%
Seong Huiju.

01:10:12.842 --> 01:10:14.677 line:80%
[♪ tense music plays]

01:10:18.723 --> 01:10:19.724 line:80%
Seong Huiju.

01:10:32.737 --> 01:10:35.281 line:80%
-[exhales sharply]
-[clamoring]

01:10:36.490 --> 01:10:37.533 line:80%
Seong Huiju!

01:10:38.284 --> 01:10:39.368 line:80%
Huiju.

01:10:45.041 --> 01:10:47.251 line:80%
Huiju. Seong Huiju.

01:10:50.963 --> 01:10:52.298 line:80%
Seong Huiju!

01:11:01.724 --> 01:11:04.643 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

01:11:40.763 --> 01:11:43.099 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>Toxicity? Me?</i>

01:11:43.182 --> 01:11:44.767 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] <i>It looks deliberate.</i>

01:11:45.476 --> 01:11:47.853 line:80%
I knew you would fail to protect her.

01:11:47.937 --> 01:11:49.438 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>I made a mistake.</i>

01:11:49.522 --> 01:11:51.065 line:80%
What are you doing? Calm down!

01:11:51.148 --> 01:11:53.442 line:80%
He's in danger right now!

01:11:53.526 --> 01:11:55.528 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>Was I being too greedy again?</i>

01:11:56.862 --> 01:11:58.405 line:80%
<i>You're okay, right?</i>

01:11:58.489 --> 01:11:59.740 line:20%
<i>I thought you were dying.</i>

01:12:00.407 --> 01:12:01.742 line:20%
<i>I thought I lost you.</i>

01:12:02.243 --> 01:12:03.744 line:20%
What are you doing?

01:12:03.828 --> 01:12:06.580 line:20%
<i>The whole country saw me collapse live.</i>

01:12:06.664 --> 01:12:08.749 line:20%
<i>I can't be this pretty</i>
<i>when I'm discharged.</i>

01:12:09.583 --> 01:12:11.794 line:20%
[I-AN] <i>It's our first night</i>
<i>as a married couple.</i>

01:12:12.419 --> 01:12:13.462 line:20%
<i>Are you ready?</i>

01:12:19.093 --> 01:12:20.636 line:20%
EPILOGUE

01:12:20.719 --> 01:12:21.720 line:20%
Don't make…

01:12:24.056 --> 01:12:25.558 line:20%
things difficult for Huiju.

01:12:26.642 --> 01:12:27.643 line:20%
What?

01:12:27.726 --> 01:12:29.353 line:20%
That's not

01:12:30.688 --> 01:12:31.814 line:20%
what she wants from you.

01:12:42.032 --> 01:12:43.075 line:80%
[sighs]

01:12:43.701 --> 01:12:45.077 line:20%
Then why wasn't it you?

01:12:48.581 --> 01:12:50.708 line:20%
What she aims to gain through marrying me.

01:12:52.084 --> 01:12:53.460 line:20%
You could provide the same.

01:12:59.758 --> 01:13:01.343 line:20%
Perhaps I have something

01:13:02.469 --> 01:13:03.512 line:20%
she wants

01:13:05.097 --> 01:13:06.098 line:20%
that you don't have?

01:13:20.196 --> 01:13:22.198 line:20%
Translated by Justin S. Kim

01:13:33.500 --> 01:13:37.213 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN